{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "7f6d6f6b-8f7a-4b1f-9b3c-2f8a3e8b6f21",
    "name": "CitySec - Seguridad",
    "description": "Colección para certificar el MVP del módulo Seguridad (RBAC): Roles + Permisos (solo lectura).\n\nVariables de colección:\n- baseUrl: URL base del backend (ej: http://localhost:3000)\n- apiVersion: versión del API (ej: v1)\n- token: JWT (se llena automáticamente con Login)\n- rolId: id del rol para GET/PUT/DELETE y gestión de permisos\n- permisoSlug: slug de permiso a buscar (ej: usuarios.usuarios.read)\n- permisoId: id del permiso obtenido por slug (se llena automáticamente)\n\nPermisos RBAC involucrados:\n- usuarios.roles.{create,read,update,delete}\n- usuarios.roles_permisos.assign\n- usuarios.permisos.read\n\nNotas:\n- Todas las rutas requieren autenticación (verificarToken).\n- Los endpoints de permisos están en modo solo lectura en este MVP.\n",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Auth",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Login (guarda token)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"username_or_email\": \"admin\",\n  \"password\": \"Admin123!\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/{{apiVersion}}/auth/login",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "{{apiVersion}}", "auth", "login"]
            }
          },
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "const json = pm.response.json();",
                  "const token = json?.token || json?.data?.token || json?.accessToken || json?.data?.accessToken;",
                  "if (token) pm.collectionVariables.set('token', token);",
                  "pm.test('Login responde 200/201', function () {",
                  "  pm.expect([200, 201]).to.include(pm.response.code);",
                  "});"
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Permisos (solo lectura)",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Listar permisos (GET /permisos)",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{token}}" }],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/{{apiVersion}}/permisos?limit=50&activos=true",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "{{apiVersion}}", "permisos"],
              "query": [
                { "key": "limit", "value": "50" },
                { "key": "activos", "value": "true" }
              ]
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Permisos por módulo (GET /permisos/modulo/:modulo)",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{token}}" }],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/{{apiVersion}}/permisos/modulo/usuarios",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "{{apiVersion}}", "permisos", "modulo", "usuarios"]
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Buscar permiso por slug (GET /permisos/slug/:slug) (guarda permisoId)",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{token}}" }],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/{{apiVersion}}/permisos/slug/{{permisoSlug}}",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "{{apiVersion}}", "permisos", "slug", "{{permisoSlug}}"]
            }
          },
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "const json = pm.response.json();",
                  "const id = json?.data?.id || json?.id;",
                  "if (id) pm.collectionVariables.set('permisoId', String(id));",
                  "pm.test('Responde 200', function () {",
                  "  pm.expect(pm.response.code).to.eql(200);",
                  "});"
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "Obtener permiso por ID (GET /permisos/:id)",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{token}}" }],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/{{apiVersion}}/permisos/{{permisoId}}",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "{{apiVersion}}", "permisos", "{{permisoId}}"]
            }
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Roles",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Listar roles (GET /roles)",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{token}}" }],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/{{apiVersion}}/roles?limit=50&activos=true",
